<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .otp-container {
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      color: #e05a4a;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #fff3f0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="<%= process.env.LOGO_URL || 'https://e-commerce-jatin.vercel.app/logo.png' %>" alt="Company Logo" class="logo"/>
      <h1>Reset Password</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>

      <p>We received a request to reset your password. Use the OTP (One-Time Password) below to proceed:</p>

      <div class="otp-container">
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
      </div>

      <p>This OTP is valid for only 5 minutes. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>

      <div class="note">
        <p>For your security, never share this code with anyone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Eshop. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Sonipat, India</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
